sted by the Science of Language.'' (Transl. by Alexander V. W. Bikkers) London, J. C. Hotten (1869) * ''A Compendium of the Comparative Grammar of the Indo-European, Sanskrit, Greek, and Latin Languages'', translated from the third German edition by Herbert Bendall. London: Trübner and Co (1874) (Actually an abridgement of the German original.) * ''Laut- und Formenlehre der polabischen Sprache.'' reprinted by Saendig Reprint Verlag H. R. Wohlwend, {{ISBN|3-253-01908-X}} * ''Sprachvergleichende Untersuchungen.'' reprinted by Minerva GmbH, Wissenschaftlicher Verlag, {{ISBN|3-8102-1072-2}} * ''Die Formenlehre der kirchenslavischen Sprache erklaerend und vergleichend dargestellt.'' Reprint by H. Buske Verlag, Hamburg (1998), {{ISBN|3-87118-540-X}}
